<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Can anyone help me understand the ending? Antehai leaves his overcoat - why? And, he is the only one that did not bow when she exited the tomb - what is the significance of that? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
