<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think it was a silent and discrete invitation to the Empress to enjoy her life and make out with that general. He did not bow because he was an acco<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think it was a silent and discrete invitation to the Empress to enjoy her life and make out with that general. He did not bow because he was an accomplice now. He was the only one to know her secret. I expect him to be the same devoted and faithful servant but still...<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
