          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780747579922" href="/book/show/862345.Empress_Orchid">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6163718-rusalka?shelf=around-the-world">around-the-world</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6163718-rusalka?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>, 
