        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer428514975" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16104442876501653951">This book is filled with drama, intrique, loyalty, corruption, forbidden love and mystery. The Forbidden City is a totally different world for the book&apos;s heroine, Orchid, who becomes one of the Emperor&apos;s wives at the age of 17. Ms. Min has written a spellbinding novel, with colorful and interesting characters, rich detail and a vivid, interesting history of China, complete with details on customs, rituals and distictions between the Manchu&apos;s and the Chinese. Orchid and her eunech, An-te-hai will</span>
  <span id="freeText16104442876501653951" style="display:none">This book is filled with drama, intrique, loyalty, corruption, forbidden love and mystery. The Forbidden City is a totally different world for the book's heroine, Orchid, who becomes one of the Emperor's wives at the age of 17. Ms. Min has written a spellbinding novel, with colorful and interesting characters, rich detail and a vivid, interesting history of China, complete with details on customs, rituals and distictions between the Manchu's and the Chinese. Orchid and her eunech, An-te-hai will keep the reader spellbound. This is the first book that I've read by Ms. Min and I couldn't put it down!!</span>
  <a data-text-id="16104442876501653951" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


