<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/47305.The_Last_Empress"><img alt="The Last Empress (Empress Orchid, #2)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1433552246l/47305._SY75_.jpg" />
